2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531765-20200612.htm&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrj%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=8183b602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531765-20200612.htm&h=ea18a72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531765-20200612.htm</a><br />\n任志剛：對聯匯制度信心十足 沽空港元將損手離場<br />\n他接受中通社專訪時表示，近期因資金流入港元，匯率徘徊接近強方兌換保證，指出沽空港元賭聯匯失守的投機者，一如以往將損手離場。他奉勸投資者，不要踏入找理由為客戶做港元沽空、同時賺取昂貴費用的基金管理人圈套。"},{"pid":"e2a917e6b88edc30510f9ece37bea0104de7ec98","tid":2062555,"uid":337899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ac5dc244831de6e8cf1fa23c207c026ba83ee57","tid":2062555,"uid":33336,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大鱷操作唔係咁沽港元<br />\n<br />\n散戶跟機可以用你個玩法<br />\n<br />\nP loan 約5-6厘息，睇你點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T00:49:04.000Z","msg":"邊有炒家借p loan, 只有h"},{"pid":"e5e38d4014a61f370042d352a2cd784fa1a9f852","tid":2062555,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T00:51:43.000Z","msg":"所謂國際大行同投機者點沽空港幣?<br />\n<br />\n你自己去睇吓一年後遠期港元期貨/期權而家個價係點先<br />\n<br />\n而家息口低, 港元係超穩健0風險, 咁時間值損耗同vol都係超低, 對遠期期權持倉人嘅成本係好著數<br />\n<br />\n玩過炒外滙margin, 都知呢D FX 合同係幾多倍槓桿, 何況人吔仲係賭期權, 只有up side only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n駛乜咁On9去借P loan?<br />\n<br />\n樓主係咪做緊財仔想搵生意?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 借港元買美元係一個cash out散水走資嘅方法, 好多有錢佬都用呢個咁簡單嘅財技走資<br />\n<br />\n不過D有錢佬係將名下物業, 寫字樓, 商舖, 樓同車位打包抵押, 做按揭或term loan, 咁個息可以好低H+0.5 / P-3 之類, 借長錢再換美元/外幣去海外買美元債/股/樓...甚至搞生意都得<br />\n<br />\n你班中產港豬頂多係同層樓加按套現走資, 稅貸都唔好諗, 千祈唔好借短錢/高槓桿咁玩, 隨時係你爆倉時港元都未爆"},{"pid":"fcfca88ee21b681d64d482aeb52597d6b7c6af4d","tid":2062555,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"推！就輸！"},{"pid":"17bc2912bc5559cbbad6ec8061e2f9286f3a50db","tid":2062555,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"全民黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe63161112651bfb7aabb13507d9414a3753fdc1","tid":2062555,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"其實美國唔比港元掛鉤美元，只要重有足夠外匯儲備，掛一籃子貨幣，港元兌美元都唔一定跌"},{"pid":"f105be52071d6c51b3015f9bee3d72e6ccaf3166","tid":2062555,"uid":130209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19eda431208867b9358a5f204ad9a09b2d4283ac","tid":2062555,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69c17ed62304d58220cb65361712bf11be50a600","tid":2062555,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"1.借錢(港幣)<br />\n2.換美金 or 其他貨幣<br />\n<br />\n快D沽啦攬炒契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T00:32:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531765-20200612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531765-20200612.htm&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrj%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=8183b602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531765-20200612.htm&h=ea18a72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531765-20200612.htm</a><br />\n任志剛：對聯匯制度信心十足 沽空港元將損手離場<br />\n他接受中通社專訪時表示，近期因資金流入港元，匯率徘徊接近強方兌換保證，指出沽空港元賭聯匯失守的投機者，一如以往將損手離場。他奉勸投資者，不要踏入找理由為客戶做港元沽空、同時賺取昂貴費用的基金管理人圈套。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi